title: JAN 28 2022 - PRESIDENT OF UKRAINE SLAMS PRES. BIDEN AFTER BOTCHED CALL
description:
The president of Ukraine slams President Biden after having to correct him multiple times on their recent phone call, President Biden prepares shortlist for the Supreme Court pick, Sweden has decided against recommending Covid vaccines to children ages 5-12, and a new survey data from the Manhattan Institute shows that Americans under 30 lean towards cultural socialism. 




Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
